"""
actual-amazon-noter - Update Actual Budget transaction notes with Amazon order details

This script correlates Amazon transaction records from CSV exports with
transactions in Actual Budget, then updates the Notes field with Amazon order details.

Usage:
    actual-amazon-noter [--dry-run [json] | --execute] [--days X] [--force]
        [--actual-http-api URL | --actual-http-api-file /path/to/URLfile]
        [--actual-http-api-key SecretKey | --actual-http-api-key-file /path/to/SecretKey]
        [--actual-syncid SyncID | --actual-syncid-file /path/to/SyncID]
        File.csv File2.csv ...

For full documentation, see Overview.md, Status.md, and USAGE.txt
"""

